{"tid":1179094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普宣布對墨西哥進口貨加徵5%關稅    直至經墨西哥進入美國的非法移民潮結束為止","createTime":"2019-05-31T01:05:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T05:37:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7a0307076c9b66493671091c2f2c2532ddc8790e","tid":1179094,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:05:15.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普宣布，下月10日起對所有來自墨西哥的貨品，開徵5%的關稅，直至經墨西哥進入美國的非法移民潮結束為止。特朗普又說，非法移民問題一日未解決，對墨西哥的關稅會逐漸增加，有關詳情白宮稍後會公布。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1111570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1111570&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=21197f85\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1111570</a>"},{"pid":"acbc04ec5d091d164b0ddfae2fa81fd9367b3666","tid":1179094,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:07:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36896952bc59cc68756ecaf316c47858335c539","tid":1179094,"uid":40470,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:08:52.000Z","msg":"即係墨西哥打手板<br />\n<br />\n強國人就大大力兜巴星<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">贏！</span></span>"},{"pid":"bfa5406375b8a0727f7b106804f460ac88b61c5e","tid":1179094,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:13:41.000Z","msg":"其實即係要人比回扣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370c8a0b18457bea3e810bf65f1838033bb5f2c5","tid":1179094,"uid":228532,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:23:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd31cf68593d6b290b76a50bddca28177c1798a2","tid":1179094,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":