徵關稅   (講明支持美國打擊非法移民, 但反對美國向墨西哥加徵關稅)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thehill.com/homenews/senate/446278-grassley-slams-trump-tariffs-on-mexico?__twitter_impression=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fhomenews%2Fsenate%2F446278-grassley-slams-trump-tariffs-on-mexico%3F__twitter_impression%3Dtrue&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=c24a6854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thehill.com/homenews/senate/446278-grassley-slams-trump-tariffs-on-mexico?__twitter_impression=true</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSenate Finance Committee Chairman Chuck Grassley (R-Iowa) condemned President Trump's new tariffs on Mexico late Thursday, calling the move a &quot;misuse&quot; of presidential tariff authority and cautioning that they could derail passage of the United States Mexico Canada Agreement (USMCA).<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Trade policy and border security are separate issues. This is a misuse of presidential tariff authority and counter to congressional intent,&quot; Grassley said in a statement.<br />\n<br />\nThe lawmaker cautioned that following through on Trump's tariff threat &quot;would seriously jeopardize passage of USMCA,&quot; a revision of the North American Free Trade Agreement (NAFTA).<br />\n<br />\n&quot;I support nearly every one of President Trump&rsquo;s immigration policies, but this is not one of them,&quot; he added."},{"pid":"fa07ccda2f5f09546c74ee98d9b2157e0e6f5ef5","tid":1179094,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:28:52.000Z","msg":"Trump 個twitter 被左膠日日輪姦<br />\n好癲"},{"pid":"24d7122374f008ca0c3674c6536b0c50ce94383c","tid":1179094,"uid":23120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:37:28.000Z","msg":"1838年爆發糕點戰爭。1848年在美墨戰爭戰敗後，墨西哥被迫把北部大片的土地售予美國（面積相當於美國現今南方的七個州份）。1853年的加茲登購地又使墨西哥失去7萬多平方公里的土地。"}]}